1974;;The Black Godfather;;American;;John Evans;;Rod Perry;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Black_Godfather;;J.J. (Rod Perry), a rising star in the black crime scene, is in the process of consolidating his power over the neighborhood. One of the only remaining obstacles is the white heroin cartel that is understandably reluctant to abandon such a lucrative market. Tensions rise, and an explosive confrontation is the result.